Steps to creat a files in terraform and push to github repo
1) cd ~/Documents/terraform
2) git init
3) touch .gitignore 
4) In .gitignore (add following commands)
aws/
*.zip
terraform.tfvars
*.tfvars
.terraform/
terraform.tfstate
terraform.tfstate.backup
5) touch provider.tf  (add following commands)
provider "aws" {
  region = "ap-south-1"
}
6) variables.tf   (add following commands)
variable "aws_access_key" {
  type = string
}

variable "aws_secret_key" {
  type      = string
  sensitive = true
}
7) terraform init
terraform plan
8) git remote add origin https://github.com/Razain21/Terraform_codes.git
9) git add .
10) git commit -m "added terraform code"
11) git branch -M main 
12) git push -u origin main
